[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 0.8"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

The following security holes affect Tails 0.8.

We **strongly** urge you to [[upgrade to Tails 0.8.1|news/version_0.8.1]]
as soon as possible in case you are still using an older version.

Details
=======

These are Debian security announces; details can be found on the
[Debian security page](http://security.debian.org/):

  - iceweasel (DSA-2313-1)
  - linux-2.6 (DSA-2310-1)
  - openoffice.org (DSA-2315)
  - policykit (DSA-2319)
